XPath-Tools

fx - Find XPath query
=====================
Generate short paths for accessing a specific string in a given page.

Show generated queries only.
cat doc.html | fx 'search string'

Show generated queries with percentage string match (length based, very simple)
cat doc.html | fx -p 'search string'

Show generated queries with percentage match and fetched content
cat doc.html | fx -p -c 'search string'

xp - Run XPath query
====================
Run Xpath query on a HTML/XML document and show the results.

xp doc.html '//text()'
